"### Actions \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"7 (1d10 + 2) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Breath Weapons (Recharge 5â€“6).** The dragon uses one of the following "
"breath weapons.    \n"
"**Fire Breath.** The dragon exhales fire in an 20-foot line that is 5 feet "
"wide. Each creature in that line must make a DC 11 Dexterity saving throw, "
"taking 14 (4d6) fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a "
"successful one.    \n"
"**Sleep Breath.** The dragon exhales sleep gas in a 15-foot cone. Each "
"creature in that area must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or "
"fall unconscious for 1 minute. This effect ends for a creature if the "
"creature takes damage or someone uses an action to wake it.\n"
